{"tid":315280,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係愛另一半多過愛自己","createTime":"2017-07-10T01:53:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T06:27:09.000Z","uid":96878,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1247586737bcc1d71ed7d205ebb33b7f88e7636","tid":315280,"uid":96878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T01:53:39.000Z","msg":"即係佢好似冇乜點為我諗過 永遠都只顧自己<br />\n但相反我就事事以佢為先 做咩都顧及佢感受先<br />\n其實咁樣拍拖真係好辛苦 <br />\n不過我真係好愛佢 唔想因爲咁樣而分手<br />\n有冇人巴絲明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e136f390ceb05ac7fd591ac6ba1af2ab02d59f98","tid":315280,"uid":3935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T02:00:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係佢好似冇乜點為我諗過 永遠都只顧自己<br />\n但相反我就事事以佢為先 做咩都顧及佢感受先<br />\n其實咁樣拍拖真係好辛苦 <br />\n不過我真係好愛佢 唔想因爲咁樣而分手<br />\n有冇人巴絲明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有時會覺得你會咁諗既其實咪又係愛自己多d"},{"pid":"e9ce049f2d2700728b2fcb3cf52eb2c90af98389","tid":315280,"uid":6962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T06:45:41.000Z","msg":"我明<br />\n永遠都係下把位<br />\n但我又甘心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係想佢對我好啲"},{"pid":"29c250d9a45c1726afbb6383adf3e3ae8150e815","tid":315280,"uid":84369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T06:55:37.000Z","msg":"好睇愛自己果方仲愛唔愛你<br />\n唔愛&gt;你付出&gt;佢覺得有負擔有壓力&gt;想分手<br />\n早啲同對方傾下個問題啦<br />\n<br />\n利申 同樣情況 被飛"},{"pid":"3fa9ddcd86ed5b632ca2918d5597ab9b90ef09cf","tid":315280,"uid":28052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T06:58:27.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢搵我個時就算我幾唔得閒/開心緊都會聽佢電話陪佢傾計先 但係佢唔會<br />\n同埋洗錢係佢到洗好多 佢中意我都會買比佢<br />\n相反我想要都唔會買 除非有需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc62863ecf2e6c854098a246bbc1a4b8890a2660","tid":315280,"uid":23736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T12:09:45.000Z","msg":"成日覺得自己一味為佢付出得太多 太重視佢<br />\n但感覺上佢並唔係咁著緊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似單方面得我一個努力緊去維持喱段關係咁<br />\n真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba8d5d4d5dfe10f911c86612e816655037247e2d","tid":315280,"uid":73762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T12:10:44.000Z","msg":"我明 諗緊分唔分好"},{"pid":"224309555fc8a537e7ca3f336d50664982027d1e","tid":315280,"uid":90839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T12:28:05.000Z","msg":"已經分左"},{"pid":"5bf13d9d1a881bf10548e77fbf5f1f3eb061d42c","tid":315280,"uid":29283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T12:37:11.000Z","msg":"同感 一樣辛苦 好唔健康"},{"pid":"6acc501cacca5752a606003f40f4a80fdd58b4e2","tid":315280,"uid":30710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T12:44:56.000Z","msg":"以後都唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4673af3cb9346cf3d8d192bd16877a68f7e9ccec","tid":315280,"uid":30395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T12:57:21.000Z","msg":"曾經都係咁 結果分手"},{"pid":"102ec3d301637026a23298e4e52ca50ee094af27","tid":315280,"uid":82234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T12:58:56.000Z","msg":"I know that feel"},{"pid":"16deb1092f3c55a2adf085c25e67f98f6243e3d3","tid":315280,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T12:58:59.000Z","msg":"控制吓自己啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"851695347abb724acc5606dee1c8248950480ed1","tid":315280,"uid":9647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T13:13:49.000Z","msg":"愛一個陌生人多過愛自己"},{"pid":"1f7cf818057144f17e4283347e6c6109e76acf7a","tid":315280,"uid":46457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T13:17:14.000Z","msg":"感情本來就唔平等<br />\n諗佢為你做過乜不如諗下你為佢做到乜<br />\n佢開心咪得<br />\n係辛苦d 架喇，付出好似冇回報咁"},{"pid":"c07cd4e4b74609ec538b5e55da796d68bde277ca","tid":315280,"uid":20436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T13:22:55.000Z","msg":"當你既愛 係佢眼中變成負擔壓力<br />\n結果就兩敗俱傷<br />\n係唔適合既 趁早分開/攤牌<br />\n<br />\n利申：被分手<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">你冇可能睇到 睇到都唔會點 但我真係好痛好痛 點解你完全唔念在呢半年既感情</span></span>"},{"pid":"11a34ac3382518fb26bc2450291e71dd68db0027","tid":315280,"uid":20696,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T13:28:09.000Z","msg":"有時候覺得自己嘅愛太洶湧太澎湃<br />\n可以為佢付出所有，做咩都係諗佢先，遠遠超過愛自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但其實有時會覺得咁樣唔好<br />\n有時候唔係佢唔愛唔夠愛，係我自己太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者熱戀期過去，佢懶左我無懶<br />\n好容易不平衡，或者因為付出得越多渴求越多<br />\n可能我減少少大家就會最舒服，但明明我嘅愛係咁多，勉強自己減少好無謂，咁我仲拍黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c4932998d5f837061067523c46ef6d6a285012","tid":315280,"uid":26850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T14:42:13.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣 啱啱被分手"},{"pid":"8d0c418d5a7acf5af58d3e2d1786836529af78f5","tid":315280,"uid":73650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T15:43:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20578057a3acfd4663d22101b5db9f4fb25bed65","tid":315280,"uid":57624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T15:53:53.000Z","msg":"我都係完完全全係咁 啱啱散 好心痛 好心痛 真係好痛好痛"},{"pid":"fde4a2fed752a55e3c9ce860b76ad2c302c3255c","tid":315280,"uid":126704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T15:57:21.000Z","msg":"我差d以為個post我開 完全一樣"},{"pid":"cdb58bf23dbb7c4b147937b333437ade6596c409","tid":315280,"uid":24235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T17:06:32.000Z","msg":"我愛佢多過佢愛我<br />\n最後佢覺得好大壓力 散左兩個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d53b1070756538b41fe22b